{"tid":950490,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺焗西米布甸好撚好食?","createTime":"2018-12-21T14:34:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-26T15:06:27.000Z","uid":175988,"like":39,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4d2d73d973c101f702559bca1e22920b6dc3938d","tid":950490,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T14:34:08.000Z","msg":"<strong>蓮苑 @ K11</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/POUkh1K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FPOUkh1K.jpg&h=7f511245&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>蓮蓉西米焗布甸</strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n布甸外貌飽滿，表層微焦帶光澤，齋睇已經<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n西米份量算外，整體食落軟滑，唔會過杰或者過稀，帶淡忌廉同奶香<br />\n蓮蓉甜度適中，同布甸幾㚒，唔會搶咗各自嘅味道<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蛋香味唔夠，唔好俾布甸咁靚嘅色水呃到<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n價錢偏貴，成四十幾五十蚊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我俾盡都只值$30-$35<br />\n<br />\n<strong>結論: 過吓口癮都ok，特登來就不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong>"},{"pid":"696574c6de66dd25df1702561250d4ef6034352d","tid":950490,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T14:34:55.000Z","msg":"*算多"},{"pid":"aef314334fb8f7b3b3939344a0e034165765d658","tid":950490,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T15:01:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee560fc91024d40585accf771fc05a8fb4b10445","tid":950490,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T16:04:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b12c9c6aa7e8045e4f30db43ea75d88b2a0dc91","tid":950490,"uid":104669,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T16:54:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 勁鍾意食<br />\n細個美心有蓮蓉底嘅西米布甸<br />\n而家變左栗子<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c6ee0554a0216cb8a84d922d14bb41cbc832c33","tid":950490,"uid":160774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T17:16:05.000Z","msg":"以前長沙灣間新星酒樓個個好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47db09343eedf15c78d8711f7bf600810ebe522c","tid":950490,"uid":175988,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T02:48:09.000Z","msg":"大家覺得滿記個焗布甸點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0404c3cbb6d5036cc02b8d72a6acfb47d152779d","tid":950490,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T07:11:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"948b721e118cf1546a770e36e815cd85d13a92e3","tid":950490,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T11:21:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2738f5a3d348bde7b1483c2fa705d823ca8482d9","tid":950490,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T11:35:55.000Z","msg":"如果冬至飯有焗布甸食就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b066f26369ad2339dd59cf2d273abb21948473a8","tid":950490,"uid":155815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T12:16:50.000Z","msg":"就咁焦糖雞蛋布甸先係世一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ad8f20c0f4f83c3326b6fc5911e84ca12706e61","tid":950490,"uid":175988,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b066f26369ad2339dd59cf2d273abb21948473a8","tid":950490,"uid":155815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T12:16:50.000Z","msg":"就咁焦糖雞蛋布甸先係世一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTi